      <li>Device Information: Information about the device you use to access the app, such as device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    The information we collect is used to:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li>Provide and maintain the app.</li>
      <li>Improve the app's functionality and user experience.</li>
      <li>Display personalized advertisements through Google AdMob.</li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">3. Data Security</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. All data is encrypted and protected using industry-standard measures.
  </p>

  <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1.5rem;">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
    We use third-party services to enhance the functionality of our app, including but not limited to:
    <ul style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
      <li><b>Google AdMob:</b> Used to display advertisements within the app. AdMob may collect and use data as outlined in their privacy policy.</li>
      <li><b>Riot Games API:</b> Used to track player data and game statistics. Riot Games API collects data as outlined in their privacy policy.</li>
    </ul>
